OL,3,CEid celebrations take place as fasting
OL,4,Cmonth of Ramadan ends
OL,6,FAround 3,000 Muslims in west Belfast
OL,7,Fhave marked the end of Ramadan and the
OL,8,Fbeginning of Eid-al-Fitr.
OL,10,FThe religious event, which translates
OL,11,Fto 'the festival of breaking the
OL,12,Ffast', marks the end of a period of 30
OL,13,Fdays of fasting.
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland's biggest event was
OL,16,Fheld at an indoor sports pitch at
OL,17,FColin Glen Leisure Park.
