OL,6,FEid is a time when families and
OL,7,Ffriends gather to eat and spend time
OL,8,Fwith one another following the dawn-
OL,9,Ftil-sunset fasting period.
OL,11,FAsim Sattar explained how Eid is
OL,12,Fcelebrated.
OL,14,F"It will last another two days and all
OL,15,FMuslims, invite non-Muslims as well,
OL,16,Finto their houses and show their
OL,17,Ftraditions."
