OL,3,CEid celebrations take place as fasting
OL,4,Cmonth of Ramadan ends
OL,6,FIt was a morning full of peaceful
OL,7,Fwishes but Islam is a faith that has
OL,8,Fcome under attack in Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fin recent times.
OL,11,FOn two occasions within the last few
OL,12,Fyears, in January 2021 and April 2022,
OL,13,FBelfast Multi Cultural Centre in south
OL,14,FBelfast was targeted by arsonists.
OL,16,FMuhammad Atif is from the centre.
OL,18,F"It felt like our whole dream was in
OL,19,Fthe fire, I didn't know what we were
OL,20,Fgoing to do," he said.
