OL,6,F"We had big plans at that point, it
OL,7,Fwas very uncertain."
OL,9,FMuhammad commended the Belfast
OL,10,Fcommunity for rallying round Muslims
OL,11,Fat that time.
OL,13,F"Within a couple of days, the way the
OL,14,FBelfast and wider Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fcommunity came together to help us. It
OL,16,Fwas unbelievable."
OL,18,FHe added that action needs to be taken
OL,19,Ffrom government level to help protect
OL,20,Fminority communities.
